var __index = {"config":{"lang":["en"],"separator":"[\\s\\-]+","pipeline":["stopWordFilter"]},"docs":[{"location":"index.html","title":"H10 Visualizer","text":"<p>Documentation for the H10 Visualizer.</p>"},{"location":"getting_started.html","title":"Getting Started","text":""},{"location":"getting_started.html#install-docker","title":"Install Docker","text":"<p>You can find the instruction in the official website: docker.com</p>"},{"location":"getting_started.html#download-h10_visualizer-repo","title":"Download h10_visualizer Repo","text":"ghgit clone <pre><code>cd ~\ngh repo clone lora3a/h10_visualizer\n</code></pre> <pre><code>sudo apt install git\ncd ~\ngit clone https://github.com/lora3a/h10_visualizer.git\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"getting_started.html#build-custom-docker-images","title":"Build Custom Docker Images","text":"<p>Info</p> <p>The building process can be done only the first time, unless you delete the docker container images.</p> <p>Inside the <code>h10_visualizer</code> folder:</p> <pre><code>docker compose build\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"getting_started.html#run-docker-compose","title":"Run Docker-Compose","text":"<pre><code>docker compose up -d\n</code></pre>"},{"location":"getting_started.html#visit-grafana-dashboard","title":"Visit Grafana Dashboard","text":"<p>Visit localhost:3000</p>"},{"location":"getting_started.html#when-done","title":"When Done","text":"<ol> <li> <p>Stop Docker Compose</p> <pre><code>docker compose down\n</code></pre> </li> <li> <p>Remove created volumes</p> <p>Note</p> <p>Check docker volumes:</p> <pre><code>docker volume ls\n</code></pre> <pre><code>DRIVER    VOLUME NAME\nlocal     h10_visualizer_grafana_data\nlocal     h10_visualizer_postgres_data\n</code></pre> <pre><code>docker volume rm [volumes]\n</code></pre> <p>Tip</p> <p>If you can't remove the volumes:</p> <pre><code>docker volume rm --force [volumes]\n</code></pre> </li> </ol>"}]}